items.headline: #1 Course 100% Dedicated  to Helping YOU Build Self Esteem & Self Confidence. Become Self Confident Today!
objectives_summary: How do you build self-esteem and self-confidence? Designed by a motivational coach and published author this course will take you through a journey of theory to help you understand important concepts you need to know, and organised easy to do techniques that you can apply with the least amount of time and effort.

Through our compassionate, light hearted, and non-judgemental training you are going to discover from our experienced and trusted instructors why you are not alone, society's constrictions that holds you back, and how to raise Self-Esteem and how to gain Self-Confidence to levels you never thought was possible.

First we will dig into THE THEORY BASICS: What is self-confidence and self-esteem, what is healthy and unhealthy body image, how the mind works, the importance of finding your WHY, habit formation, why you need to change focus from weight to self, what is self-love and why it is important, and much, much more!

items.title: Personality Disorders:  Types and Treatments
items.headline: Ten Personality Disorders and Therapies
objectives_summary: Know how to identify and distinguish the ten different Personality Disorders that are defined in the DSM-5. Students will learn the best psychotherapeutic methods for treating these personality disorders. You will also work through examples that will enable you to test your knowledge of PDs and how psychotherapy can help them. Finally, we will review the key concepts regarding PDs that include clusters of symptoms, definitions and demographics.
